          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2320.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2320.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2320.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Trim the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong> and chop them in half, then add them to a<strong> food processor</strong> and blitz for 30 secs or until finely shredded</p><p>Tip: Don't have a food processor? Slice them finely instead!</p><p>Add the<strong> shredded sprouts</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them until bright green and wilted, then set aside to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2320.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
