            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2320.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>baby button mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> with the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until softened – these are your<strong> 'bacon' mushrooms</strong></p>",
